des: WYZE-I is the Internet version of WYZE Radio based in Atlanta, Georgia. WYZE-I plays a broad mix of Gospel Music: Traditional, Urban, Contemporary and Classics. WYZE-I also highlights Local Atlanta Artist. Listen!!! You will be inspired and your soul stirred.
